    "body": "Hi @aymeric-giraudet It seems like next.js with its addInsertedHtml function causes a memory leak issue. If I comment out insertHTML call the memory leak is gone that of course breaks SSR. Have you considered not using ServerInsertedHTML but return <script> from the component JSX if it's possible?",
